issue.title: [CF 1243] Warlock Resource Bug in v8.0.3
issue.body:
TMW Version: v8.0.3
Profile export: http://pastebin.com/UdBXWHBx

Hello! Awesome addon!

I have been using TMW for a while now. With the launch of 7.0.3 and the addon's update however, I am facing a slight error on my warlocks.

When the addon loads (login/reload) I get a message saying "Equivalencies.lua:473: processing" in the chatbox. Closer investigation also shows that the Soul Shard option seems slightly bugged but behaves alright.

Screenshot: http://bit.ly/2a7EFkM

The bug doesn't seem critical in any fashion, but it does cause some quality of life inconveniences. If it could be fixed I would be a very very happy man!

Thank you and keep up the good work.


> Posted by CurseForge user anty2004gr | Imported from CurseForge issue #1243 | Raw
